diff:1385405606:1385370322:=289,293d288%0a%3c !!Moon Phases%0a%3c * The current moon phase on the chat is the same as the real world. Anyone who wants to know the current moon phase can check the following lunar calendar: http://www.moonconnection.com/moon_phases_calendar.phtml%0a%3c %0a%3c * This also means that every moon phase receives three nights before shifting to the next moon phase. This allows werewolves three nights to reap lunar benefits such as extra essence and increased ability with shapeshifting.%0a%3c %0a
