diff:1385063572:1384720425:=142,143d141%0a%3c http://www.cgw.com/images/media/News/Marc/DarkShadowsAfter-Castle.jpg%0a%3c %0a145,174d142%0a%3c %0a%3c * The Grounds: The grounds outside the estate are covered in green and fenced off. The area is reasonably secluded from outside eyes and allows many hiding places to shapeshift without witnesses.%0a%3c %0a%3c * The Main Hall: This is the greeting hall where visitors to the family estate are greeted by the Wolf-Blooded and Skinchangers living here. This entryway has several hallways leading to other parts of the estate.%0a%3c %0a%3c * West-Wing: The western wing of the estate is mostly filled with bedrooms. They are luxurious and comfortable, offering soft beds and shelter for family members who are looking for a place to stay.%0a%3c %0a%3c * East-Wing: The eastern wing of the estate is where you'll find the library, study, kitchens, dining room, and the office for the current Family Head. It is easily the busiest section of the house with family members moving between the various rooms to handle dinner preparations, study up on the occult, or practice their taxidermy.%0a%3c %0a%3c '''Resonance:''' Secrets%0a%3c Territory: Skidaway Island (Keepers of the Marsh Territory)%0a%3c %0a%3c !!The Pinkerton Station%0a%3c '''District:''' Historic District%0a%3c %0a%3c %25width=730%25http://i.imgur.com/5HTMT2w.jpg %0a%3c %0a%3c Kitchen open 24/7 %0a%3c %0a%3c No alcohol 3 AM to 7AM Monday through Saturday.%0a%3c No Alcohol 2:55 AM Sunday til 7 AM Monday%0a%3c %0a%3c Badges, guns, and police man blue dominate the bar. The police of Savannah tend to congregate at this bar after their shifts. People with warrents or gang colors quickly find themselves interrogated or arrested if they wander into the bar.%0a%3c %0a%3c Ironically enough a number of small crimes happen daily in The Pinkerton Station perpetuated by the police. Police officers will usually be playing cards and gambling at a table. Underage servers, always of direct relation to police officers, will stay clocked in once the liquor starts flowing and keep serving patrons. Children can often be spotted on a bar stool being supervised by the bartender as they wait for their police parents to get off shift.%0a%3c %0a%3c * The Backroom: There is a room located in the back of the kitchen where raw meat is served to werewolves with a developed taste for flesh and blood. The room bares a resemblance to a slaughter house with "delicacies" hanging on hooks from the ceiling. The floor is outfitted with grates to allow for blood to be easily hosed down the drains from the carnivorous appetites of its patrons. It is a place where werewolves can shed their skins and enjoy a meal out-of-sight of the Herd.%0a%3c %0a%3c '''Resonance:''' Hunger\\%0a%3c '''Territory:''' This diner is considered neutral ground claimed as part of the Hegemony's protectorate.%0a
